{
  "texts": [
    "The two sub-networks were connected by feeding the features extracted from each into a triplet loss function.",
    "Fashion retrieval can help customers to select coordinating fashion items from a massive dataset of fashion items in the Metaverse based on the attributes and characteristics of the items.",
    "Identifying deformed fashion items and mapping cross-domain attributes are currently research hotspots in the field of fashion retrieval.",
    "Exploring the controllability provided by attribute disentanglement and retrieval of unlabeled fashion items is also a worthwhile avenue for future work.",
    "Many people like to ask friends to accompany them when shopping, to help them evaluate the clothes they choose and provide suggestions."
  ]
}